data.description: Welcome to your "Oasis" in one of the happiest cities in America!  Come see this gorgeous open floor plan so that you can enjoy the stunning Lake view across the Oasis of a back yard.  Quaintly located in the heart of Naples just about 15 minutes to anywhere you need to be in town.  Beautiful Oversized Pergola!  Newly sodded 4 years ago and perfectly kept landscaping ever since all around the house! Granite counters in the kitchen, mud room, island in kitchen, and Master BR.  Custom wood trim throughout the home.  Additional storage and closet space added to the Master BR.  There has been a Murphy Bed added to the office/bedroom as well that matches the cabinets and desk!  New privacy fence in the backyard. Electric hurricane shutters along the back and side of the house.  Tennis Courts, Pickleball courts, and a POOL just a short walk away!  The home is Rear facing Southern exposure.    DO NOT miss this Beautiful Gem of a home in Naples, FL!!!   Super low HOA expenses in Berkshire Lakes!
